    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拆箱与发现</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打开箱子，找到各种物品和家具，每一件都揭示了你的客户的生活和个性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/73f89cff5fcf8fd38369901e2f24c001.poster.avif?t=1765200537\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/73f89cff5fcf8fd38369901e2f24c001.webm?t=1765200537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/73f89cff5fcf8fd38369901e2f24c001.mp4?t=1765200537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由装饰</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从沙发到小杯子，随心所欲地布置，创造出让人感到舒适和亲近的空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/697220c96647b8fa2d6baeee73c85a02.poster.avif?t=1765200537\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/697220c96647b8fa2d6baeee73c85a02.webm?t=1765200537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/697220c96647b8fa2d6baeee73c85a02.mp4?t=1765200537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简单的故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过客户带来的物品了解他们的过去、习惯和梦想。当你帮助他们安顿下来时，他们的家悄悄地诉说着他们的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/e01e3f05bbd9b6cb6e39f5b9160c1d2f.poster.avif?t=1765200537\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/e01e3f05bbd9b6cb6e39f5b9160c1d2f.webm?t=1765200537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/e01e3f05bbd9b6cb6e39f5b9160c1d2f.mp4?t=1765200537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻松的游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有分数、计时器或竞争的压力，你可以尽情整理和装饰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/fafd77e401e86a1985714e79b707c443.poster.avif?t=1765200537\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/fafd77e401e86a1985714e79b707c443.webm?t=1765200537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/fafd77e401e86a1985714e79b707c443.mp4?t=1765200537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沙盒模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个模式下，你可以自由地尝试已经拆开的物品和家具。释放你的想象力，将虚拟空间打造成个性化的避风港！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/330e862e3b8af6960a811b35de3c679f.poster.avif?t=1765200537\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/330e862e3b8af6960a811b35de3c679f.webm?t=1765200537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017730/extras/330e862e3b8af6960a811b35de3c679f.mp4?t=1765200537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Unbox the Room 中，享受让新家变得温馨而满足的宁静感觉吧！</p>",
